item.title: Help pl0x!
item.dc:creator: @pasta186 pasta186
item.description:
@pasta186 wrote:

Okai
Right click on your compiler
Click edit
Then press ‘control and a’ to highlight all that text

Then change all that text with this:

@echo off
javac *.java
pause

(this is why the mod commented this) Then close the compiler(make sure to save!!) and try that.
